  "intent": "Execute a redo replacement picking protocol using a Greiner Masterblock 384-well plate (225\u00b5L capacity) and Eurofins 96x2mL tube rack. For each specified tube-to-well transfer pair, first aspirate the designated disposal volume (default or specified per sample) from the destination well using multiple 280\u00b5L cycles with 20\u00b5L air gaps, dispensing waste to trash. Then transfer the specified volume (default or per sample) from the source tube to the cleared well using the same air gap technique. Maintain slow Z and A axis speeds during aspiration, with bottom clearances of 0.7, 0.4, 0.2, and 0mm for complete removal.",
